						               													<description>Kronocell is a two-player skirmish miniatures game that combines strategy, bluffing and positional play. With time being a main component, combat doesn't rely on dice rolls, large decks of cards or complicated rules. Featuring an elegant Action/Reaction mechanic, Turns are shared between players, creating a fluid action experience.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;By strategically maneuvering your Units and using Command Cards you will lay waste to your opponent, attacking and countering his moves, while at the same time gaining control over vital Control Points scattered around the Battlefield.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Kronocell is geared towards war and strategy gamers that enjoy deep, while easy and fluid gameplay. Unit stats feature only Movement and Health Points, but the underlying Action System allows for a highly diverse and unique gameplay of each Unit.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
